Helene has facilitated face-to-face language exchange workshops at the Club
d'échange linguistique de Montréal language school (CELM) in Montreal, Canada
for over 3 years. Her workshops have earned great praise among her <a href="WorkshopsTestimonials.asp">students</a> for being truly unique and effective 
as well as being thoroughly enjoyable and fun. As a result, many of her students have been repeat customers. Also, many new students
were referred by language teachers from the local universities, such as McGill
University and Concordia University. She even had referrals from other private language
schools in the city.<br><br>

